"><div class="media-object-interactiveLink"><div class="image-container"> <a class="interactive-link" href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/childrens-books-unlikely-companions-and-memorable-adventures-75cc3015"><img width="16" height="10" src="https://images.wsj.net/im-815638?width=700&amp;height=467" alt="不明确的" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><span class="image-interactive-icon">
            </span></a></div><div class="wsj-article-caption">乔恩·克拉森 (Jon Klassen) 插图，摘自《头骨：蒂罗尔民间故事》<span class="wsj-article-credit">烛芯</span></div></div></div><p>另外还有《孩子与河》、《抓小龙虾、数星星》和《滚滚，小豌豆》。<em>梅根·考克斯·格登的评论</em></p><p><a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/childrens-books-unlikely-companions-and-memorable-adventures-75cc3015?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">阅读评论</a></p><div class="media-object scope-web|mobileapps
